# 💪 Egoist Miscellaneous

Madmate and Neutrals won't be Egoist. If the Egoist's team wins, the Egoist wins instead of his team.

  • Max
    • Set the Maximum amount of Egoists that can be in a match
  • Spawn Chance
    • Set the percentage players have of getting Egoist
  • Crewmates can become Egoist
    • ON: Crewmates can become this role
    • OFF: Crewmates cannot become this role
  • An Impostor can become Egoist
    • ON: Impostors can become this role
    • OFF: Impostors cannot become this role
  • Impostors Can See Other Egoist Impostor
    • ON: an Impostor can see the Egoist, and an Egoist can see the Impostor like normal
    • OFF: the Impostor has no clue of his Egoist teammate
